	   <tr><td colspan=2>First of all I have to say that unless you buy your Direct Damage line of spells and get your skills up, you will always regret it and your life as a druid will likely be a miserable time for you. Honestly you NEED them.<br>As for where to go and what to hunt at level 10, go to West Commonlands and fight willowisps, bears and if you get a group fight the orcs.<br>But before you do any of that, buy your direct damage spells, target yourself and repeat nuke yourself or someone's pet if they will let you and get your evocation skill maxed.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
